00:02:10.760 --> 00:02:12.720
YOUR MAJESTY ARRIVES

00:02:24.760 --> 00:02:26.720
Paying respects to Your Majesty.

00:02:27.480 --> 00:02:28.600
All ministers, rise.

00:02:29.080 --> 00:02:30.960
Thank you, Your Majesty.

00:02:31.720 --> 00:02:33.320
Present your matters.

00:02:33.680 --> 00:02:35.640
If there's nothing, court is dismissed.

00:02:36.320 --> 00:02:37.240
Your servant.

00:02:38.040 --> 00:02:39.080
I have a memorial.

00:02:40.760 --> 00:02:42.600
It's rare for Prime Minister Ming to submit a memorial.

00:02:42.920 --> 00:02:44.000
Let me hear it.

00:02:44.280 --> 00:02:45.240
What is it about?

00:02:45.560 --> 00:02:46.880
I report

00:02:47.080 --> 00:02:49.320
General of the North, Nan Hongyi,

00:02:49.800 --> 00:02:52.200
violated the rites set by the Late Emperor,

00:02:52.600 --> 00:02:55.680
concealing his son Nan Chenxiao's true gender.

00:02:55.920 --> 00:02:57.240
Such intent deserves punishment.

00:03:01.960 --> 00:03:02.400
Majesty...

00:03:02.680 --> 00:03:03.320
Your Majesty.

00:03:03.840 --> 00:03:05.080
There is absolutely no such thing!

00:03:05.800 --> 00:03:06.400
Prime Minister Ming,

00:03:06.720 --> 00:03:08.400
