00:03:08.800 --> 00:03:10.720
This concerns the previous dynasty.

00:03:10.920 --> 00:03:13.400
How could I speak carelessly about it?

00:03:14.520 --> 00:03:15.360
Your Majesty.

00:03:16.520 --> 00:03:18.240
Yesterday, my family

00:03:18.440 --> 00:03:21.280
was attacked at our estate outside the city.

00:03:21.840 --> 00:03:23.920
After capturing the culprit,

00:03:24.200 --> 00:03:25.000
I discovered

00:03:25.840 --> 00:03:29.400
