00:03:29.800 --> 00:03:31.200
A Da Yue killer.

00:03:32.320 --> 00:03:34.240
After my interrogation,

00:03:34.600 --> 00:03:35.800
I learned these Da Yue people

00:03:36.120 --> 00:03:37.880
took such risks

00:03:37.920 --> 00:03:39.240
to come to Ling An

00:03:40.320 --> 00:03:43.120
not only to assassinate King Wurong,

00:03:43.360 --> 00:03:44.440
but also to seek

00:03:44.880 --> 00:03:46.800
revenge on the one who killed their king,

00:03:46.960 --> 00:03:49.480
Young Master Beicheng.

00:03:51.240 --> 00:03:52.240
He confirmed

00:03:53.240 --> 00:03:55.000
the one married to Second Rank Grand Scholar

00:03:55.640 --> 00:03:57.000
Rui Yu,

00:03:57.280 --> 00:03:59.640
Nan Chenxiao, the only daughter of the Nan family,

00:04:00.880 --> 00:04:02.040
is actually

00:04:02.880 --> 00:04:04.680
Young Master Beicheng.

00:04:05.360 --> 00:04:08.600
The Young Master Beicheng King Wurong sought is her.

00:04:09.480 --> 00:04:10.600
Isn't she a woman?

00:04:10.920 --> 00:04:12.680
So she is Young Master Beicheng.

00:04:19.080 --> 00:04:19.800
Your Majesty.

00:04:20.720 --> 00:04:22.440
Nan Chenxiao is already my wife.

00:04:22.680 --> 00:04:24.680
I know her best.

00:04:25.520 --> 00:04:27.640
The Nan family's son died at the border.

00:04:28.520 --> 00:04:30.560
How can we trust such a schemer's accusation?

00:04:30.680 --> 00:04:32.040
How can it be believed?

00:04:32.280 --> 00:04:33.400
Whether it's true or not,

00:04:33.720 --> 00:04:35.200
just bring Nan Chenxiao here,

00:04:35.200 --> 00:04:36.120
and everything

00:04:37.000 --> 00:04:38.800
will be clear.

00:04:39.040 --> 00:04:39.840
Your Majesty.

00:04:40.320 --> 00:04:41.080
Your servant.

00:04:41.080 --> 00:04:41.880
I have followed

00:04:42.200 --> 00:04:43.320
the Late Emperor's order

00:04:43.680 --> 00:04:45.560
to investigate the exile of military officers.

00:04:46.240 --> 00:04:47.320
Due to my oversight,

00:04:47.520 --> 00:04:49.720
the Nan family kept this child.

00:04:49.960 --> 00:04:51.680
It has caused trouble until now.

00:04:52.440 --> 00:04:54.560
They not only hid their identity,

00:04:54.760 --> 00:04:56.000
deceived the sovereign,

00:04:56.400 --> 00:04:58.520
but also brought Wurong and Da Yue people.

00:04:58.640 --> 00:04:59.480
In our country,

00:04:59.880 --> 00:05:01.280
