00:05:01.320 --> 00:05:02.880
and act recklessly.

00:05:03.320 --> 00:05:04.040
Fortunately,

00:05:04.200 --> 00:05:05.600
it hasn't led to disaster.

00:05:06.080 --> 00:05:09.080
Please summon Nan Chenxiao to the palace quickly,

00:05:09.640 --> 00:05:11.640
to verify her identity.

00:05:23.600 --> 00:05:24.560
Your Majesty.

00:05:30.560 --> 00:05:31.680
Do as Prime Minister Ming says.

00:05:32.520 --> 00:05:32.960
Li Quan.

00:05:33.000 --> 00:05:34.360
Your old servant will go at once.

00:06:07.200 --> 00:06:08.200
Reporting to Your Majesty,

00:06:08.560 --> 00:06:09.960
