00:06:10.800 --> 00:06:11.320
Rui's wife—

00:06:11.640 --> 00:06:12.080
No,

00:06:12.240 --> 00:06:13.280
Nan Chenxiao

00:06:13.520 --> 00:06:14.680
is indeed male.

00:06:14.920 --> 00:06:15.400
What?

00:06:15.440 --> 00:06:16.520
A man?

00:06:17.240 --> 00:06:17.600
A man?

00:06:17.680 --> 00:06:19.320
How bold!

00:06:22.920 --> 00:06:24.120
Nan Hongyi,

00:06:25.080 --> 00:06:26.360
do you know

00:06:26.760 --> 00:06:28.640
violating the Late Emperor's order

00:06:29.280 --> 00:06:30.920
and deceiving the sovereign

00:06:31.880 --> 00:06:34.480
is a crime punishable by extermination of the nine clans!

00:06:37.640 --> 00:06:40.760
I beg Your Majesty to punish us.

00:06:46.800 --> 00:06:47.600
Nan Chenxiao.

00:06:48.280 --> 00:06:49.440
I personally decreed

00:06:49.720 --> 00:06:51.240
your marriage to Rui Yu.

00:06:51.720 --> 00:06:53.000
All under heaven know

00:06:53.080 --> 00:06:54.960
I arranged this marriage.

00:06:55.800 --> 00:06:58.440
Today you confess before all officials,

00:06:59.600 --> 00:07:01.600
do you mean to shame me?

00:07:01.920 --> 00:07:03.800
I beg for punishment of the Nan family.

00:07:07.640 --> 00:07:08.240
Your Majesty.

00:07:08.560 --> 00:07:09.680
Your servant is willing to accept

00:07:09.680 --> 00:07:10.240
the punishment for the Nan family.

00:07:14.440 --> 00:07:15.160
Reporting to Your Majesty,

00:07:15.480 --> 00:07:16.720
Prince of Pingxiang sent a secret letter.

00:07:17.160 --> 00:07:18.120
Regent King Hou Qi

00:07:18.320 --> 00:07:19.680
leads troops to besiege Pingxiang Palace.

00:07:20.080 --> 00:07:21.560
Requests our dynasty to send reinforcements.

00:07:28.200 --> 00:07:28.800
Your Majesty

00:07:29.200 --> 00:07:31.080
Our court just formed a new alliance
with Pingxiang.

00:07:31.160 --> 00:07:32.080
To set an example,

00:07:32.080 --> 00:07:33.360
we must send troops to assist.

00:07:33.440 --> 00:07:35.440
Only then can we bring peace
to all lands.

00:07:36.800 --> 00:07:38.000
The Left Minister speaks wisely.

00:07:38.560 --> 00:07:40.200
Sending troops is not up for debate.

00:07:41.160 --> 00:07:42.000
However,

00:07:42.240 --> 00:07:43.760
the position of commander

00:07:44.280 --> 00:07:45.920
should be given to whom?

00:07:49.680 --> 00:07:50.480
Your Majesty,

00:07:51.120 --> 00:07:52.520
though the Nan family is guilty,

00:07:53.040 --> 00:07:55.720
on the Pingxiang battlefield,

00:07:55.880 --> 00:07:57.200
none of the generals present

00:07:57.280 --> 00:07:59.000
know it as well as General Nan.

00:07:59.600 --> 00:08:01.880
Let General Nan atone with merit.

00:08:02.200 --> 00:08:03.720
The guilty Nan Chenxiao
will serve in the army.

00:08:04.120 --> 00:08:05.480
Let them serve the nation.

00:08:06.040 --> 00:08:06.840
Absurd!

00:08:07.480 --> 00:08:09.480
War is no child's play.

00:08:09.640 --> 00:08:11.760
The Nan family deceived
Your Majesty—a capital crime.

00:08:12.240 --> 00:08:13.440
Rui Yu, your words

00:08:13.880 --> 00:08:15.960
