00:08:16.120 --> 00:08:17.160
The battlefield is perilous.

00:08:17.800 --> 00:08:18.520
Moreover,

00:08:18.720 --> 00:08:20.320
we are only aiding Pingxiang.

00:08:21.000 --> 00:08:22.240
The Nan family is already guilty.

00:08:22.840 --> 00:08:24.880
If anything happens in battle,

00:08:25.080 --> 00:08:26.920
it serves as their punishment.

00:08:28.080 --> 00:08:29.880
Reducing Ling An's losses

00:08:29.960 --> 00:08:31.560
is our top priority.

00:08:32.400 --> 00:08:33.680
What does the Left Minister think?

00:08:35.200 --> 00:08:35.760
Your Majesty,

00:08:36.320 --> 00:08:38.600
the border is in crisis.

00:08:38.800 --> 00:08:41.280
Since General of Manifest Valor
fell for the nation,

00:08:41.680 --> 00:08:45.200
no young talent has emerged at court.

00:08:45.480 --> 00:08:48.600
I believe the Nan family
should atone by leading the army.

00:08:48.760 --> 00:08:49.800
For Ling An,

00:08:50.440 --> 00:08:51.600
to relieve our troubles.

00:08:52.080 --> 00:08:52.960
If so,

00:08:53.120 --> 00:08:54.040
Nan Chenxiao

00:08:54.120 --> 00:08:55.080
will join the army at once.

00:08:55.320 --> 00:08:56.040
Nan Hongyi

00:08:56.360 --> 00:08:57.600
will marshal troops to Pingxiang.

00:09:01.760 --> 00:09:02.560
However,

00:09:02.720 --> 00:09:04.560
